
                                README
                 for the images accompanying the work

                        Classroom Examples of
            Robustness Problems in Geometric Computations
                                  by
              Lutz Kettner, Kurt Mehlhorn, Sylvain Pion,
                     Stefan Schirra, and Chee Yap

         <http://www.mpi-sb.mpg.de/~kettner/proj/NonRobust/>


This directory contains the images in PNG format resulting from the
experiments done with the ../src/fp_scope_ext program as explained in 
the ../src/Experiments.txt file. 


